{"expireTime":9007200845181201000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-3495f7c5668c9985f73551a2ae493637--","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Volume 1, Issue 14","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":19,"offset":19},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":19,"offset":19},"indent":[]}},{"type":"html","value":"<br>","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":21},"end":{"line":4,"column":5,"offset":25},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What's New This Week","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":5,"offset":31},"end":{"line":6,"column":25,"offset":51},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":27},"end":{"line":6,"column":25,"offset":51},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Welcome back and thanks for joining us again in the Winter Hearth Epic Life Playbook, where each week we explore the human experience through different mediums, gleaning useful and practical insights to become more socially and emotionally powerful. ","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":52},"end":{"line":7,"column":251,"offset":302},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":52},"end":{"line":7,"column":251,"offset":302},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Following last week's digest, ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":9,"column":31,"offset":334},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"/newsletters/volume-1/curiosity-driven-life","children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Curiosity-Driven Life","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":32,"offset":335},"end":{"line":9,"column":57,"offset":360},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":31,"offset":334},"end":{"line":9,"column":103,"offset":406},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":", this week is all about the Gift of Gratitude. Gratitude is powerful. Gratitude has the power to transform entire mindsets from negative and hopeless to positive and optimistic. To be truly grateful is to appreciate every aspect of life, taking the good with the bad, and choosing to use it to move forward rather than to stay in the same place or to regress. Gratitude allows us to be humble and to understand that there are forces in this world beyond our control, and also to understand that neither our successes nor our failures come completely by our own hands. The gift of gratitude is a gift of healthy perspective, and a healthy perspective is key to enhancing your reality (check out our edition on The Pursuit of Perspective here for more on the topic).","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":103,"offset":406},"end":{"line":9,"column":868,"offset":1171},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":9,"column":868,"offset":1171},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"If you're reading this edition, I'm immensely grateful that you've committed time and energy to support this endeavor of mine, and I really hope that you have been inspired and empowered by the content I write for you each week.","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":1173},"end":{"line":11,"column":229,"offset":1401},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":1173},"end":{"line":11,"column":229,"offset":1401},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"As always, there's plenty of content here, so feel free to just take what you need.","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":1403},"end":{"line":13,"column":84,"offset":1486},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":1403},"end":{"line":13,"column":84,"offset":1486},"indent":[]}},{"type":"html","value":"<div class='text-center pt-20 pb-20'>\n    <img src='https://gallery.mailchimp.com/82935